Company Overview of FleetOne Holdings, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
FleetOne Holdings, LLC through its subsidiary offers fuel cards, trucking and transportation services, and wholesale and export of petroleum products. FleetOne Holdings, LLC was formerly known as TransPlatinum Service Corp. The company was founded in 1988 and is based in Nashville, Tennessee. As of October 4, 2012, FleetOne Holdings, LLC operates as a subsidiary of WEX Inc.


